column5: Hey guys, going to a cottage on Rosseau Lake tomorrow in the Muskokas, anyone fished it or a simliar lake in the area lately?  Any info is great...  Thanks  Matt
There's smallies, pike, some lakers, the odd walleye and some muskie in there. Bring an assortment of gear and you should be covered.
BIG PIKE !  BIG LAKERS !  Go deep and go slow ...
